content: Preparing for the NCCAOM exam is a big undertaking, but with adequate study and preparation, you should be well-equipped to pass it. It's also important to remember that the education and clinical training you receive in acupuncture school will provide you with a strong foundation for your future practice, and the hands-on experience you gain during your clinical hours will be invaluable for developing your skills and confidence as an acupuncturist. Best of luck to you on your journey!
